[The serotype of _S. enterica_ involved in this outbreak is mentioned
in the Illinois Department of Health Press release as (Serotype I
4,5,12,i-). It appears that the outbreak may be multistate but
ProMED-mail awaits additional information that the outbreak organism
is the same. - Mod.LL]

